#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:16
msgid "Graph mode is currently available only on the **V1 Engine**."
msgstr "图模式目前仅在 **V1 引擎** 上可用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:17
msgid ""
"**ACLGraph** (capture/replay via `torch.npu.NPUGraph`) is the runtime "
"graph execution mechanism used by the default graph path on Ascend."
msgstr "**ACLGraph**（通过 `torch.npu.NPUGraph` 捕获/重放）是 Ascend 上默认图路径使用的运行时图执行机制。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:18
msgid ""
"**Npugraph_ex** is a compile-time FX graph optimization layer, enabled by"
" default in FULL/FULL_DECODE_ONLY modes. It optimizes the graph before "
"ACLGraph captures it."
msgstr ""
"**Npugraph_ex** 是一个编译时 FX 图优化层，在 FULL/FULL_DECODE_ONLY 模式下默认启用。它在 "
"ACLGraph 捕获图之前对其进行优化。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:19
msgid ""
"**XliteGraph** is an optional graph path for selected model families and "
"environments."
msgstr "**XliteGraph** 是针对选定模型系列和环境的可选图路径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:20
msgid ""
"In context parallel scenarios, `cudagraph_mode=\"FULL\"` is not "
"sufficiently supported yet."
msgstr "在上下文并行场景中，`cudagraph_mode=\"FULL\"` 尚未得到充分支持。"

