#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:49
msgid "Using ACLGraph"
msgstr "使用 ACLGraph"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.md:51
msgid ""
"ACLGraph is the runtime graph capture/replay mechanism on Ascend. It is "
"enabled automatically when graph mode is active (i.e., `cudagraph_mode` "
"is not `NONE`), and does not require explicit configuration."
msgstr ""
"ACLGraph 是 Ascend 上的运行时图捕获/重放机制。当图模式激活时（即 `cudagraph_mode` 不是 "
"`NONE`），它会自动启用，无需显式配置。"

